high_descs: Turn around and walk to the watering can on the floor by the fireplace.
Pick up the watering can from the floor.
Turn left and walk forward to the lamp on the desk to the right of the chair.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a watering can by the light of a desk lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk around the coffee table to face space between the desk and the fireplace.
Pick up the tea kettle from off of the floor.
Turn around, go to the right, and go straight to face the small brown table in the corner.
Turn the lamp on that's on the brown table.
anns.task_desc: Turn the lamp on that's on the table while holding the tea kettle.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the left corner of the fireplace.
Pick up the teapot from the floor.
Turn left and move to the side table in the corner of the room next to the white chair.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at the teapot by the light of the lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the watering can between the dresser and fireplace.
Pick up the watering can on the floor.
Turn left and walk towards the coffee table with the small lamp on it.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a watering can by the light of a lamp on a coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the tea pot on the floor near the fireplace.
Pick up the tea pot from the floor.
Turn around and walk over to the table near the chair with the cell phone on top of it.
Turn on the lamp on the table.
anns.task_desc: Turn the light on while holding the tea pot.

high_descs: Turn directly around and face the white watering can on the floor
Pick up the white watering can from the floor
Turn left and walk past the TV and stand in front of the table in the corner of the room
Turn the lamp on while still holding the watering can
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp while holding the watering can
